title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Installing flybywire A32NX
description:
In this how to we are going to look at how to use install and use the AS32NX addon created by FlybyWire.

This addon replaces the default cockpit, sounds, aircraft behavior and much more for Airbus A320 which is part of Microsoft Flight Simulator 2020.

AS320NX can be downloaded from this site: https://flybywiresim.com/a32nx
